    {
      "name": "⚡ QUICK TEST SEQUENCE",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "🚀 Run All Tests in Order",
          "request": {
            "description": "⚠️ IMPORTANT: Execute requests in this order:\n1. Create Tenant 1\n2. Create Tenant 2\n3. Register User 1 (Tenant 1)\n4. Register User 2 (Tenant 2)\n5. Create Restaurant 1 (User 1)\n6. Create Restaurant 2 (User 2)\n7. List Restaurants (User 1) - Should only see Restaurant 1\n8. List Restaurants (User 2) - Should only see Restaurant 2\n9. Get Restaurant 1 (User 1) - Should succeed ✅\n10. Get Restaurant 1 (User 2) - Should fail with 404 ❌ (This validates multi-tenant isolation!)",
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/health",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["health"]
